title: OOK 55300 Double Headed Picture Hangers, 4 in 1 Bear Claw Screw Hooks, 100lbs (12 Piece)
description: Display pictures of your proud moments securely with these OOK bear claw four-in-one screw hooks. The steel construction ensures durability, while the bear claw pattern works with D-rings, sawtooth hangers and keyholes for versatile mounting options. With the included mounting hooks, these hangers are easy to keep level and can hold weights of up to 100lbs. These OOK bear claw four-in-one screw hooks come in a 12-pack for an ample supply.
